LOUXOR FOR PETS 
For those who seek the finest for their beloved companions, Baccarat, with daring creativity, has imagined the Louxor for Pets Collection. 

Designed by Thomas Bastide, the Louxor Pet Bowl draws inspiration from the grandeur of ancient Egypt. Adorned with intricate diamond-cut crystal motifs, it captures light and elevates your pet’s routine with elegance and joy.

@Baccarat, bringing pleasure into the world of our four-legged friends.

Set design by @joeandnathan
